- Eureka server an application that holds the information about all client service application
- Eureka server is also an eureka client
- Used to locate multiple server in our distributed network
- Helps to identify failured services in distributed network
- Provides Loadbalancing 

Dependencies:
- Eureka Discovery Client
- Eureka Server

# Steps
 - Create the Project
 - Add Eureka Server Dependency
 - Enable Eureka Server
 - Configure the properties
 - Test
